    <briefdescription>
<para>This file contains a design example using the Xilinx SCU Private Watchdog Timer driver (<ref refid="struct_x_scu_wdt" kindref="compound">XScuWdt</ref>) and hardware device in watchdog mode. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This test illustrates how to initialize the watchdog device and restart it periodially to avoid the assertion of the WDRESETREQ pin.</para><para><simplesect kind="note"><para>None.</para></simplesect>
MODIFICATION HISTORY:</para><para><preformatted>
  Ver   Who  Date     Changes
<hruler/>

  1.00a sdm  01/15/10 First release
  2.5   asa  07/18/23 Added support for workflow decouplig flow.
                      Interrupt wrapper support has also been added.
  2.5   dp   09/08/23 Update example to stop wdt at end of the test
  2.7   vlt  12/29/25 Update Doxygen comments to include SDT flow details.
*</preformatted> </para>    </detaileddescription>
